\c 6
\s1 Iyyov’s first response to Elifaz
\p
\v 1 Then Iyyov \add (Job) responded\add*:
\q1
\v 2 If only my anguish could be truly weighed,
\q1 and my calamity could be \add put\add* together \add with it on the scales\add*.
\q1
