\q1 and the clods of soil stick together?
\b
\q1
\v 39 Can you hunt for prey for the \bd lioness\bd*,
\q1 and satisfy the appetite of \add her\add* cubs,
\q1
\v 40 when they crouch in their dens—
\q1 lying in wait in the thicket?
\b
\q1
\v 41 Who prepares prey for the \bd raven\bd*
\q1 when its chicks cry out to God for help,
\q2 \add when\add* they stagger around for lack of food?
\b
\c 39
\q1
\v 1 Do you know when it is that \bd mountain goats\bd* give birth?
\q1 Do you watch the \add wild\add* does having their fawns?
\q1
\v 2 Have you counted how many months it’ll be after they conceived?
\q1 Do you know what date they’ll give birth?
\q1
\v 3 They crouch down to deliver their young,
