\q1
\v 18 But it doesn’t stop her flapping her wings.
\q1 She laughs at the horse and its rider.
\b
\q1
\v 19 Was it you who gave \bd the horse\bd* his strength?
\q1 Did you clothe his neck with \add that\add* mane?
\q1
\v 20 Did you make him so he can leap like a locust?
\q1 His powerful snorting is terrifying.
\q1
\v 21 They paw at the ground, excited to \add go and display\add* their strength.
